text: Chrissie Viljoen (born 11 September 1976) is a road cyclist from South Africa. She represented her nation at the 2005, 2006 and 2008 UCI Road World Championships. ==References== ==External links== * profile at Procyclingstats.com Category:1976 births Category:South African female cyclists Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
